on\n$\\Phi$. We prove De Giorgi type results and Liouville theorems for $H$-monotone\nand stable solutions in two and three dimensions when the system is symmetric.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 8 Jun 2015 23:49:17 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 31 Oct 2015 00:00:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-11-03"}
