k}$ and\n$t^{\\infty}_{\\alpha}$, which is remarkably similar to that known for fragile\nmolecular glass formers. A coupling model that accounts for the\n$t_{w}$-dependence of the stretching exponent is used to analyse and explain\nthe observed correlation between $t_{k}$ and $t^{\\infty}_{\\alpha}$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 9 Jun 2015 15:55:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-01-20"}
